Package: chRoma
Title: A Tool for Managing Vector Databases
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Win",
           family = "Cowger",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "wincowger@gmail.com")
Description: A set of tools for creating, managing, and querying in-memory vector databases. The databases can handle embeddings and metadata, support filtering by metadata, and can calculate similarities between embeddings.
